{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1112,"text":"So, my journey began\nin the Bronx, New York,"},{"time":6098,"text":"in a one-bedroom apartment,"},{"time":7890,"text":"with my two sisters and immigrant mother."},{"time":11712,"text":"I loved our neighborhood."},{"time":15382,"text":"It was lively."},{"time":16914,"text":"There was all this merengue blasting,"},{"time":19383,"text":"neighbors socializing on building stoops"},{"time":21796,"text":"and animated conversations\nover domino playing."},{"time":26327,"text":"It was home,"},{"time":28852,"text":"and it was sweet."},{"time":31368,"text":"But it wasn't simple."},{"time":33645,"text":"In fact, everyone at school\nknew the block where we lived,"},{"time":37283,"text":"because it was where people came\nto buy weed and other drugs."},{"time":41950,"text":"And with drug-dealing comes conflict,"},{"time":44544,"text":"so we often went to sleep\nto the sound of gunshots."}]},{"cues":[{"time":49839,"text":"I spent much of my childhood worried,"},{"time":53121,"text":"worried about our safety."},{"time":56803,"text":"And so did our mother."},{"time":59277,"text":"She worried that the violence we witnessed\nwould overtake our lives;"},{"time":64338,"text":"that our poverty meant"},{"time":66087,"text":"that the neighbors with whom\nwe lived and shared space"},{"time":68786,"text":"would harm us."},{"time":70851,"text":"Our entire life was in the Bronx,"},{"time":74566,"text":"but my mother's anxiety\nspurred her into action,"},{"time":77586,"text":"and soon we were driving\nso fast to Connecticut --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":82380,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":83476,"text":"to boarding school campuses,\nwith full scholarships in tow."},{"time":87857,"text":"Man, don't underestimate\nthe power of a mother"},{"time":93615,"text":"determined to keep her children safe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97010,"text":"(Cheers)"},{"time":98316,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":103553,"text":"At boarding school,"},{"time":106658,"text":"for the first time,"},{"time":109867,"text":"I was able to sleep without worry."},{"time":113391,"text":"I could leave my dorm room unlocked,"},{"time":115968,"text":"walk barefoot in the grass,"},{"time":118291,"text":"and look up to see\na night sky full of stars."},{"time":124061,"text":"Happy novelties."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127172,"text":"But there were other novelties as well."},{"time":130298,"text":"Very quickly, I felt like I didn't belong."},{"time":134469,"text":"I learned that I didn't speak\nthe right way,"},{"time":137382,"text":"and to demonstrate\nthe proper ways of speaking,"},{"time":141226,"text":"my teachers gave me\nfrequent lessons, in public,"},{"time":145759,"text":"on the appropriate way\nto enunciate certain words."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151068,"text":"A teacher once instructed me\nin the hallway:"},{"time":155040,"text":"\"Aaaaaas-king.\""},{"time":159535,"text":"She said this loudly."},{"time":162024,"text":"\"Dena, it's not 'axing,'\nlike you're running around with an axe."},{"time":167809,"text":"That's silly.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":170082,"text":"Now at this point, you can imagine\nthe snickers of my classmates,"},{"time":176258,"text":"but she continued:"},{"time":179246,"text":"\"Think about breaking the word\ninto 'ass' and 'king,'"},{"time":184667,"text":"and then put the two together\nto say it correctly --"},{"time":188720,"text":"'Asking.'\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":191918,"text":"There were some other moments\nthat reminded me that I didn't belong."},{"time":196186,"text":"Once, I walked into\na classmate's dorm room,"},{"time":200028,"text":"and I watched her watch\nher valuables around me."},{"time":204349,"text":"Like, why would she do that?\nI thought to myself."},{"time":208385,"text":"And then there was the time"},{"time":210848,"text":"when another classmate\nwalked into my dorm room,"},{"time":214311,"text":"and yelled, \"Ew!\" as I was applying\nhair grease to my scalp."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221072,"text":"There is emotional damage done\nwhen young people can't be themselves,"},{"time":226504,"text":"when they are forced to edit who they are\nin order to be acceptable."},{"time":232627,"text":"It's a kind of violence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236940,"text":"Ultimately, I'm a quintessential\nsuccess story."},{"time":241992,"text":"I attended boarding school\nand college in New England,"},{"time":245223,"text":"studied abroad in Chile"},{"time":247327,"text":"and returned to the Bronx\nto be a middle school teacher."},{"time":251027,"text":"I received a Truman Scholarship,"},{"time":253448,"text":"a Fulbright and a Soros Fellowship."},{"time":256690,"text":"And I could list more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":258598,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":260116,"text":"But I won't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261336,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":263908,"text":"I earned my doctorate\nat Columbia University."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267792,"text":"(Cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":268907,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":270737,"text":"And then I landed a job at Yale."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273103,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":275363,"text":"I am proud of everything\nthat I've been able to accomplish"},{"time":280036,"text":"on my journey thus far."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284884,"text":"I have eternal imposter syndrome."},{"time":289150,"text":"Either I've been invited\nbecause I'm a token,"},{"time":292083,"text":"which really isn't about me,"},{"time":294314,"text":"but rather, about a box\nsomeone needed to check off."},{"time":298388,"text":"Or, I am exceptional,"},{"time":301673,"text":"which means I've had to leave\nthe people I love behind."},{"time":307528,"text":"It's the price that I and so many others\npay for learning while black."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315595,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":322689,"text":"I police myself all the time."},{"time":328008,"text":"Are my pants too tight?"},{"time":330768,"text":"Should I wear my hair up or in a fro?"},{"time":334726,"text":"Should I speak up for myself,"},{"time":337195,"text":"or will the power of my words\nbe reduced to: \"She's angry\"?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":344114,"text":"Why did I have to leave the Bronx"},{"time":346748,"text":"to gain access to a better education?"},{"time":351433,"text":"And why, in the process\nof getting that better education,"},{"time":355918,"text":"did I have to endure the trauma\nof erasing what made me, me --"},{"time":363449,"text":"a black girl from the Bronx,\nraised by an Antiguan mother?"},{"time":369861,"text":"So when I think about our current\neducation reform initiatives,"},{"time":375390,"text":"I can't help asking:"},{"time":378179,"text":"What are our students of color\nlearning about themselves?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":383830,"text":"Three -- three decades of research reveal"},{"time":387141,"text":"that students of color\nare suspended and expelled"},{"time":390431,"text":"at a rate three times greater\nthan white students,"},{"time":394170,"text":"and are punished in harsher ways\nfor the same infractions."},{"time":401138,"text":"They also learn this through the absence\nof their lives and narratives"},{"time":404659,"text":"in the curricula."},{"time":407432,"text":"The Cooperative Children's Book Center\ndid a review of nearly 4,000 books"},{"time":412848,"text":"and found that only three percent\nwere about African-Americans."},{"time":418686,"text":"And they further learn this"},{"time":420073,"text":"through the lack of teachers\nthat look like them."},{"time":425550,"text":"An analysis of data"},{"time":427013,"text":"from the National Center\nfor Education Statistics"},{"time":430751,"text":"found that 45 percent of our nation's\npre-K to high school students"},{"time":435931,"text":"were people of color,"},{"time":438300,"text":"while only 17 percent of our teachers are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444881,"text":"Our youth of color pay a profound price"},{"time":447742,"text":"when their schooling\nsends them the message"},{"time":449884,"text":"that they must be controlled,"},{"time":452479,"text":"that they must leave\ntheir identities at home"},{"time":454887,"text":"in order to be successful."},{"time":459027,"text":"Every child deserves an education"},{"time":462338,"text":"that guarantees the safety to learn"},{"time":465883,"text":"in the comfort of one's own skin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":471484,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":479551,"text":"It is possible to create emotionally\nand physically safe classrooms"},{"time":484818,"text":"where students also thrive academically."},{"time":488511,"text":"I know, because I did it in my classroom"},{"time":491925,"text":"when I returned to teach in the Bronx."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495681,"text":"So what did that look like?"},{"time":499040,"text":"I centered my instruction"},{"time":501098,"text":"on the lives, histories\nand identities of my students."},{"time":506621,"text":"And I did all of this\nbecause I wanted my students to know"},{"time":509637,"text":"that everyone around them\nwas supporting them"},{"time":513348,"text":"to be their best self."},{"time":517054,"text":"So while I could not control\nthe instability of their homes,"},{"time":522321,"text":"the uncertainty of their next meal,"},{"time":525472,"text":"or the loud neighbors\nthat kept them from sleep,"},{"time":528641,"text":"I provided them with a loving classroom"},{"time":532031,"text":"that made them feel proud of who they are,"},{"time":535313,"text":"that made them know that they mattered."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539620,"text":"You know,"},{"time":542522,"text":"every time I hear\nor say the word \"asking,\""},{"time":550977,"text":"I am in high school again."},{"time":554135,"text":"I am thinking about \"ass\" and \"king\""},{"time":560117,"text":"and putting the two together\nso that I speak in a way"},{"time":564206,"text":"where someone in power\nwill want to listen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570115,"text":"There is a better way,"},{"time":572365,"text":"one that doesn't force kids of color\ninto a double bind;"},{"time":576799,"text":"a way for them to preserve their ties"},{"time":579185,"text":"to their families, homes and communities;"},{"time":582944,"text":"a way that teaches them\nto trust their instincts"},{"time":588555,"text":"and to have faith\nin their own creative genius."}]},{"cues":[{"time":595144,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596351,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}